sph.vaadin.ui

Class Theme

  • java.lang.Object
    • sph.vaadin.ui.Theme

  • public class Theme
extends Object
    Contains predefined constants pointing to the CSS class names and image resources.

    USAGE EXAMPLES:

    • Style names for Buttons: Button.addIcon(SPH_baseTheme.DELETE_ICON_16PX)
    • Theme resources for Buttons: Button.addStyleName(SMALL_BLUE_BUTTON)
    Since:
    30.10.2013
    Version:
    1.01
    Author:
    Sami Holck
